  <brief_title>Digital 3D Breast Tomosynthesis Versus 2D in Clinical Evaluation of High Risk Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>3D Digital Breast Tumorsynthesis Versus 2D Digital Mammography in the Clinical Evaluation of Women at High Risk for Breast Cancer</official_title>
